Fragtown - Bomb-Defuse

Storyline:
The town is caught in the middle of a
war on drugs between the Drug Lords group
of Terrorists and A Federal SWAT Team.

Counter Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists
from bombing the crates that contain
information on the wereabouts of the
Drug Lords crops.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the
C4 must destroy the crates that contain
information on the wereabouts of the
Drug Lords crops.

This map is dedicated to:
Anthony Wayne Hargraves
We Miss You Bro !
